attributes.title: Ep. 136 The Branch Davidians Pt. 1: Ruby Ridge
attributes.caption: The first part in our extensive series on the underground war of White Supremacists.
attributes.description: We're celebrating 1,000,000 downloads by kicking off a series that's been a long time comin'. With all the craziness surrounding the Branch Davidian's compound and violent end, it's important that we take a look at why the Feds were all shaken up. Just 9 months before everyone in America would know the town of Waco, TX, another standoff was underway. Join us as Paige takes Mando and Andrea through the Weaver Family's story and we learn why everyone was so on edge.
